{"type": "article", "id": 13313, "title": "混凝土台灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-11T06:50:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122454Tlos0J3ZjYthbcwu.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Levi Robb 一直以来对钢筋混凝土这种材料很感兴趣，他想知道当混凝土遇到设计，能发挥出什么极限。近日，他手工打造了一款混凝土台灯，灯罩厚度只有 1/8″，视觉上厚重扎实，但材料十分轻巧。而灯架设计的也别有用心，看上去就像是一个正在跳舞或是正在奔跑的小人。这是</span><a href=\"http://www.levirobb.com/\" target=\"_blank\">作者的个人主页</a><span>，点击可以查看更多作品。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140854aYyMgIGnDvl0uAq3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.36833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140854HJN1kYCtMlu49UAV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140855v89bkXPzEcd0Ly3u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140855wjTNbq9RnXA1dS0p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}